title: Mod applications
body:
Mod applications are up! I’m looking for 1-2 experienced mods as well as 1-2 jr.mods who are interested in learning the inner workings of how to mod a zine.
If you are interested in learning make sure to mention that in your application, you would have minimal responsibilities and mainly be there to watch ask questions and learn the ropes.
For everyone else applying please acknowledge that if accepted this is a large responsibility and you will be spending time every week working on this!

Here’s the link if you’re interested in applying! Only serious inquiries only please!

Applications close on March 1st

blog.name: bnhagalposts
blog.title: Bnha Headcannons and Match-ups
blog.description: Hello, Guys, Gals, and Non-binary pals! Welcome to my humble Bnha Headcanons and Match-ups! REQUESTS ARE CURRENTLY OPEN BUT, I'M ONLY TAKING HEADCANONS RIGHT NOW!!! Thank you!

summary: I really liked your headcanon for Todoroki, Midoriya, and Kaminari being picked up by their gf ❤ could you do the same for...
question: I really liked your headcanon for Todoroki, Midoriya, and Kaminari being picked up by their gf ❤ could you do the same for Bakugo, Toshinori, and Tamaki?
answer:
Bakugou:


-Bakugou being the beautiful angry boyfriend he was, currently was yelling at Kaminari since he beat him at Mario Kart. Now came in S/O who had the best plan to calm her love.

-S/O swooped Bakugou into her arms, proudly smiling at the display of her strength. “What the f*ck S/O I’m trying to talk some sense into Pikachu!”

-”Calm down honey or I’ll deprive you of kisses!” S/O smiled widely, giggling. Nuzzling her face against his cheek.

-Bakugou turned cherry red, “S/O don’t say that out loud!” He shouted out proceeding to swear afterwards.

“Ahh Bakugou likes affection.” Kaminari teased practically tempting the devil.

-”If it wasn’t for my girlfriend you would be dead.” Bakugou glared before wrapping his arms around his girlfriend’s neck, begrudging enjoying being held by her. S/O laughed before planting a kiss on his lips.


Toshinori:


-Toshinori coughed, blood starting to seep out of his lips.

-Toshinori’s S/O gasped loudly before scooping him up in her arms “Honey! Are you alright?” Toshinori then proceeded to cough more, how could his beautiful girlfriend pick him up with such ease and not even break a sweat?

-Toshinori held his hand up “I’m fine! You can put me down S/O!” His face flushed apple red.

-”Hmm, I’m thinking I like carrying you!” S/O laughed as he kept blushing harder.

-”S/O.” Toshinori hoarsely spoke out.

-”Nope! My handsome boyfriend needs to be carried!” S/O peppered his face in kisses. Toshinori truly was so lucky to have her. To have someone that cherished and loved him despite him no longer being strong, just him being skinny. Calling him handsome and didn’t even hesitate to love on him! Gosh, he needs to buy a ring already so he can propose!


Amajiki:


-Amajiki was peacefully eating fish, until some fans came up to him begging for him to turn his legs into a fishtail, making him practically a mermaid/merman. They kept persisting and it raised his anxiety to a high level. Him being someone who easily caved in when pressure turned his legs into a mermaid tail.

-His S/O arrived and frowned at him being pressured and pushed the fans away. When they were finally alone she picked him up in her arms, giving him a gentle smile.

-”You don’t have to give into that. It’s okay to say no.” S/O spoke softly, adjusting her grip around his body.

-”I- I know it’s just nerve racking when they keep pushing.” Amajiki said, burying his red face in his hands.

-S/O grinned sweetly “We’ll work on that together.” She kissed the top of his head which deepened the blush on Amajiki’s cheeks.

-”Uh. Thanks but, could you put me down now, this is embarrassing.” Amajiki sheepishly whispered. Amajiki felt ready to burst with embarrassment but, he had to admit it made he smile being in his girlfriend’s arms.  


I hope you enjoyed and have a great day! It was fun to write more strong gf being a strong gf!

Ophelia
